name: Prepare to Die Canyon
description:
Introduction

Approach

Descent

Follow the tracks for Humperdink or Lightening sands. Pass then both by heading over the saddle up onto the next smooth ridge. Head to the top staying left and descend into the obvious drainage. (Be careful not to accidentally drop in to the earlier lightening sands drainage - keep going until you see Miracle Max across the way. Then drop down).

R1 = 190' R2 = 195'

Exit

Red tape
